{"tid":1263962,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[71不舉］今時今日，你仲怕激嬲共產黨？","createTime":"2019-06-28T12:34:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T14:49:22.000Z","uid":210794,"like":126,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"84d3deb63af41a6ea5f8955ccf4c46a2c1dd9886","tid":1263962,"uid":210794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T12:34:38.000Z","msg":"自6月9以來，我哋靜坐遊行佔領，連聖詩都唱埋。結果？我哋中催淚嘅中催淚、食椒嘅食椒，甚至中彈。而林鄭依然，係依然日日龜縮喺禮賓府，日日嘆冷氣食大餐。烈士屍骨未寒，而港共第一時間做嘅竟然公然割地畀中國！佢到底當我哋係咩？<br />\n<br />\n我哋要求好過份咩？我哋只不過係想要基本尊嚴，人人天生應有嘅自由同人權。我哋只係想生存得似返個人啫？咁都唔撚得！<br />\n<br />\n林鄭，乃至背後實際主導一切嘅中國政府，七一想國慶照常升旗。升？你哋到底憑咩升，有咩值得慶祝！？<br />\n<br />\n我哋一時三刻擺脫唔到支共，但係至少，我哋唔撚會畀你開心笑住升旗！630晚，九點集結，煲底見！祝 武運亨通！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n時間:6月30號晚上9時<br />\n地點:立法會煲底<br />\n目標:金紫荊廣場<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y9x5g6u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY9x5g6u.png&h=d049462d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8yQ6LZP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8yQ6LZP.png&h=dc10d814&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1oODB6v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1oODB6v.png&h=be44a251&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FFuSGyb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFFuSGyb.png&h=632dcda7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rC9Lg6x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrC9Lg6x.png&h=67129d82&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ad82092bc6ff25ed803a5fb1234d028a3cbf0b34","tid":1263962,"uid":164190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T12:53:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2ed544fe607282c62dad844d967b32e153edb1da","tid":1263962,"uid":210794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T13:01:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a0757887fce168fc8fc8531d6b0ec1d702faa155","tid":1263962,"uid":245594,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"r